data.description: $5,000 builder incentive plus a $6,000 lender credit = $11,000 buyer credit to use towards closing costs or buy down your interest rate! Beautiful new construction development located directly across the street from Denver Heights park! An open floor plan awaits you as you walk in through the front door leading you through the dining to the kitchen. 3 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms with the downstairs bedroom having access to a full bathroom. 2 bedrooms with en-suite bathrooms are upstairs, with an additional living area and the owners' retreat offers its own private balcony. Close proximity to local downtown attractions including the Denver Heights Park that this home overlooks, San Antonio Riverwalk, Alamodome, Pearl Brewery, San Antonio Parks and Missions, AT&T Center, local restaurants, and entertainment.
